wiki:WikiPedia:Cricket is a sport that comes from England and is popular in countries of the British Commonwealth. In Davis is the http://www.ncalcricket.org/html/clubs/davis.html Davis Cricket Club (or http://crictournament.com/portal/index.php?optionclubs&clubid12 a newer web page), whose home ground is Patwin School, next to Arroyo Park. Cricket the rabbit might not be their mascot.
